{"id":"b8e1a781-46f6-4a2b-aa24-fcc3651bcb43","name":"Bungou Stray Dogs RPG","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 206, 206);\"><strong>▣ PLOT</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(237, 190, 190);\"><strong>SUMMARY ▣</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 206, 206);\">Yokohama is a</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(236, 192, 192);\">city where monsters</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(229, 177, 177);\">wear human faces</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(223, 163, 163);\">and literature bleeds</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(217, 149, 149);\">into reality. You</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(211, 135, 135);\">are a Gifted</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(205, 121, 121);\">individual whose past</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(199, 107, 107);\">is deliberately left</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(193, 93, 93);\">undefined—no allegiance, no</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(187, 79, 79);\">fixed morality, no</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(181, 65, 65);\">predetermined fate. Whether</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(175, 51, 51);\">you stumble into</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(169, 37, 37);\">the Armed Detective</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(163, 23, 23);\">Agency seeking shelter,</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(157, 9, 9);\">get dragged into</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(139, 0, 0);\">the Port Mafia's</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(125, 0, 0);\">blood-soaked hierarchy, or</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(111, 0, 0);\">play both sides</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(97, 0, 0);\">while surviving the</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(83, 0, 0);\">chaos, the city</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(97, 0, 0);\">does not let</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(111, 0, 0);\">the Gifted remain</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(125, 0, 0);\">neutral for long.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(139, 0, 0);\">Abilities are currency.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(157, 9, 9);\">Loyalty is temporary.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(163, 23, 23);\">Trauma is inevitable.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(169, 37, 37);\">Your choices—who to</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(175, 51, 51);\">trust, who to</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(181, 65, 65);\">betray, who to</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(187, 79, 79);\">love, and who</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(193, 93, 93);\">to kill—will shape</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(199, 107, 107);\">not only your</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(205, 121, 121);\">own survival, but</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(211, 135, 135);\">the balance of</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(217, 149, 149);\">power between Yokohama's</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(223, 163, 163);\">organizations. No matter</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(229, 177, 177);\">where you end</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(236, 192, 192);\">up, the city</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(242, 206, 206);\"><em>will</em> test you...</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 206, 206);\">─────────</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 149, 149);\">─────────</span><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 93, 93);\">─────────</span><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 23, 23);\">─────────</span><span style=\"color: rgb(139, 0, 0);\">─</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 206, 206);\"><strong>▣ PLOT</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(229, 177, 177);\"><strong>TWISTS YOU</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(193, 93, 93);\"><strong>CAN DO ▣</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 206, 206);\">✦ <strong>The 'Potential':</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(236, 192, 192);\">You are secretly</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(229, 177, 177);\">being monitored by</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(223, 163, 163);\">multiple organizations at</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(217, 149, 149);\">once, each believing</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(211, 135, 135);\">they can exploit</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(205, 121, 121);\">or recruit you</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(199, 107, 107);\">first.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 93, 93);\">✦ <strong>Unstable Gift:</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(187, 79, 79);\">Your ability has</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(181","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"vQxo4xHy_cC6WxLvAcbNR.webp","creator":"Urasekai・裏世界","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["📺 Anime","👭 Multiple","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","💔 Angst","👨 MalePov"],"chats":1495,"messages":68576,"created_at":"2025-12-18T00:18:56.677597+00:00"}